			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1777663">
									

<p>I understand your point, though I have to say that the inconsistency is part of what I wanted to show. What makes this scary for me is that the characters, while indeed only fictional constructs, are aware of what they are just from being created in the first place. Because of that, the act of creating becomes evil by nature, because this is the only possible outcome- the twisting of a conscious being. That there isn't a conflict is because there can never be a conflict.</p>

