			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1777696">
									

<p>I think that could work, but I don't see it in this text. It's stated explicitly that the only property a character has is the property granted to it by the author. So unless the author explicitly writes &quot;they are aware of what they are&quot;, they cannot be aware of what they are.</p>
<p>You could do a second-level meta regression there and say that the existence of <em>this</em> story is what gives them that awareness - that could also work - but that's not really present in the text as it currently is, at least to my perception.</p>

